name: Mercedes AMG GT
description:
Textual Inversion of a Mercedes AMG GT

Can produce nice images in the following scenarios:

  • moving car with motion blur

  • parked car at all angles

  • backgrounds that work best are mountains, country side, buildings

  • studio environment (white cove)

  • different car paints as the color was not trained (also matte paints)

use inpainting to get rid of rear spoiler, rim or other artifacts.

i edited out the license plates in the training data so sometimes they still show up but best case they are empty.

Trigger word is mercedes_amg_gt_ti

v1 was trained with 29 images for 3600 steps
